more relaxed and so
much more confident

00:25:39.820 --> 00:25:44.620 align:middle line:84%
as those old anxieties begin to
diminish because you know, now,

00:25:44.620 --> 00:25:46.290 align:middle line:90%
exactly how to deal with them.

00:25:46.290 --> 00:25:48.890 align:middle line:90%


00:25:48.890 --> 00:25:52.420 align:middle line:84%
And after a few times of
practicing these techniques,

00:25:52.420 --> 00:25:54.640 align:middle line:84%
those old, unwanted
responses will

00:25:54.640 --> 00:25:59.740 align:middle line:84%
change as a new response
pattern sets in,

00:25:59.740 --> 00:26:04.080 align:middle line:84%
a pattern of coping, taking
control of feeling wonderfully

00:26:04.080 --> 00:26:07.930 align:middle line:90%
relaxed and at ease.

00:26:07.930 --> 00:26:09.910 align:middle line:84%
And perhaps they're
even changing now

