And notice how you
instantly respond

00:27:27.520 --> 00:27:32.570 align:middle line:84%
in a positive, healthy way,
feeling wonderfully calm,

00:27:32.570 --> 00:27:34.160 align:middle line:90%
relaxed, and in control.

